Thanks for installing bitKlavier!

This will place the following files in your ~/Documents/bitKlavier directory:
- galleries
- soundfonts
- samples

please don't move these folders or rename the folders; bitKlavier needs them to work. It will not overwrite existing files in those folders, so your own galleries should be safe (making a backup is alway as good idea of course!).

and also the bitKlavier application will be put in your Applications folder, and the AU/VST3 plugins in your Library/Audio/Plug-Ins folder.
Enjoy!
